  "description": "A serene landscape featuring rolling hills covered in golden dry grass and lush green trees. In the distance, the iconic Golden Gate Bridge is partially obscured by a thick layer of fog, creating a dreamy and ethereal atmosphere. The fog hangs low, enveloping the surrounding hills and lending a sense of depth to the scene. The trees are a mix of evergreen and deciduous varieties, adding textural contrast. The overall composition evokes a sense of peace and tranquility.",
